PrecisEnactment of a DIRECTION TO THE CRTC (RESERVATION OF FREQUENCIES FOR TORONTO) ORDER which directs the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to reserve frequency 93.5 MHz (or another frequency on the FM band) and frequency 740 kHz on the AM band for the use of other radio services in Toronto.
